title: Print, "La Prusse", 1751
creditline: Gift of Eleanor and Sarah Hewitt
description: Escutcheon with the title of the map of Prussia in "Atlas Universel" by Robert de Vaugondy, Paris, 1757.  The top center of the map.  Rocaille escutcheon with water pouring from lateral excresences.
